{
  "stem": "3382.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The [NON-ENGLISH]-- it is commander, you know-- everybody who, who had to cut wood, and then to carry them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What they used to do, somebody cut wood, a big timber, you know, so they can put a big man like I, and put another on small one.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Pick it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "How I picked it up, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because later, I tried to pick up a much smaller thing with my brother, who is also-- was quite a guy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we couldn't even move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But, you know, at such a moment-- anyway from that [NON-ENGLISH] usually after a couple days, people would disappear.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But one day-- it was the third day I was standing with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Somebody comes up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH] it seems to me from Arbeiteinsantz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It means 'labor bureau.' And he called out-- there is no names over there, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's 509.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After I-- he went through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I stuttered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It will be the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He looked at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And [GERMAN]-- turn to the right! 50 times around the block!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I ran around the block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he-- and he stood there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the commander stood there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Schneller, schneller!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he started, you know, as if he made-- as if he hit, but he didn't hit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Schneller!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But schneller-- I got around schneller.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I made three times around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I saw the commander went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then he-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Polish-- stop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Or go to the barracks, he said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "On the upper side there on my barrack, and sleep over until the commander will return.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then register with the commander and go back to your block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We know who you are.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
